Package com.btilm305.clashapi

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AbbreviatedClan
    A representation of a clan containing data returned by most API calls.
    Clan
    A representation of all possible clan data provided by the API.
    ClanData
    The simplest representation of a Clan, containing only a few data fields.
    ClanLocation
    A representation of a location used in game.
    ClanMember
    A representation of the data of clan members.
    ClashAPI
    An API that contains operations listed at https://developer.clashofclans.com/#/documentation

    IconSet
    An interface that represents the different sizes for a single image.
    LeaderboardPlayer
    A representation of the data returned by player leaderboard API calls.
    League
    A representation of a league.
    Player
    The simplest representation of a Player.
